annotation.TEXT: Getting down from that bit was THE most terrifying thing that I've done in about 10 years. There's a split second where your feet don't touch the ground and you imagine falling 10 feet, face-first onto that granite slab below. It's not shown anywhere in this video and I didn't express it in real-life, but I'm very lucky not to be paralysed after my bag almost got stuck between those stoney sides.
